install tailwind :
1- npm init -y (init a package.json)
2-npm install -D tailwindcss
3-npx tailwindcss init (Create a Tailwind CSS config file)
add custom colors in the config file 
4-create a src folder and put inside a css file
5- ad this {npx tailwindcss -i ./src/input.css -o ./dist/output.css --watch (i for input and o for output)} into package.json in watch section
before: "test": "echo \"Error: no test specified\" && exit 1"(delete this and replace it with watch)
after :"watch": "npx tailwindcss -i ./src/input.css -o ./dist/output.css --watch"
6-add html file in src folder 
7-run the project: npm run watch
